PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FCampaigners are calling for more water
OL,7,Fmonitoring after a seven-year-old boy
OL,8,Fsuffered kidney failure and a
OL,9,Fcollapsed lung after kayaking on a
OL,10,Fbody of water in the Lake District.
OL,12,FThe family of Rex Earley, who is now
OL,13,F8, says he fell ill after around half
OL,14,Fan hour of kayaking on Windermere.
OL,16,FThe illness was identified as being
OL,17,Fcaused by E.coli, which doctors later
OL,18,Fsaid was an "isolated water borne
OL,19,Finfection".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FRex and his family, who live in
OL,7,FBradford, had been holidaying in the
OL,8,FLakes in August 2025 when they took to
OL,9,Fthe water.
OL,11,FHis mother, Claire Earley, says Rex
OL,12,Fwas later hospitalised for six weeks
OL,13,Fand underwent two emergency surgeries
OL,14,Fas a result of his illness.
OL,16,FShe told ITV News: "Hours (after
OL,17,Fkayaking) Rex became very ill... he
OL,18,Fhad really severe stomach cramps; he
OL,19,Fwas going to the toilet and told us
OL,20,Fthat it was full of blood. We knew it
OL,21,Fwas really serious then.
OL,26,@xD@[pmyD@Ipn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,F"We headed home and straight to the
OL,7,Fdoctor, who sent him straight to
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,F"Rex actually became worse, he
OL,11,Fdeveloped kidney and blood problems,
OL,12,Fand then he was transferred to high
OL,13,Fdependancy at Leeds Children's
OL,14,FHospital."
OL,16,FThis was just the start of a long
OL,17,Fordeal for Rex.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FClaire continued: "He needed an
OL,7,Femergency operation to start dialysis
OL,8,Fto save his kidneys, and he had blood
OL,9,Ftransfusions.
OL,11,F"Over the next few weeks he... he came
OL,12,Fback to us, and improved. He was sent
OL,13,Fhome, but then we realised something
OL,14,Felse was wrong, so we took him back.
OL,16,F"He had a collapsed lung. He needed a
OL,17,Ffurther operation to drain that, and
OL,18,Fthen he developed gall stones."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FClaire said the experience was
OL,7,F"traumatic", adding "not knowing what
OL,8,Fwould happen one hour to the next is
OL,9,Fsomething I won't forget in a hurry."
OL,11,FBefore her family's kayaking
OL,12,Fexcursion, Claire says she had checked
OL,13,FWindermere's water quality rating on
OL,14,Fthe Environment Agency website, where
OL,15,Fthe lake was judged as being of
OL,16,F"excellent" bathing water quality.
OL,18,FClaire told ITV News: "I was reassured
OL,19,Fby that. I thought everything would be
OL,20,Ffine, but as it happens it wasn't.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,F"You just never would expect that from
OL,7,Fa lovely day out on the water you'd
OL,8,Fend up in hospital with your son
OL,9,Fdesperately ill... it's just not on
OL,10,Fyour mind. It's this I want people to
OL,11,Fbe aware of."
OL,13,FMatt Staniek founded the group 'Save
OL,14,FWindermere' and is calling for more
OL,15,Frigorous and up-to-date testing of
OL,16,Finland waters like Windermere.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FHe said: "Accurate bathing water
OL,7,Fstatus must come about as a result of
OL,8,Frigorous testing ` the current system
OL,9,Fsimply does not do this. That's why
OL,10,FI'm campaigning for stricter, more
OL,11,Faccurate, and more regular testing."
OL,13,FRex's mother says it is impossible to
OL,14,Fknow for certain where her son
OL,15,Fcontracted the E.coli infection from
OL,16,Fbut she says the series of events is
OL,17,F"clear".
OL,19,F"He went in the water and was then
OL,20,Fvery poorly," she added.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FThe provider of water services in the
OL,7,Fnorth west, United Utilities, says its
OL,8,Fstorm overflows had not operated for
OL,9,Fover three weeks before Rex went
OL,10,Fkayaking on Windermere.
OL,12,FIt also pointed out that more than
OL,13,F1,800 septic tanks and 100 private
OL,14,Fpackage treatment plants drain into
OL,15,FWindermere.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,FA spokesperson continued: "United
OL,7,FUtilities is funding an independent
OL,8,Fstudy with a steering group to explore
OL,9,Fthe feasibility of a UK-first
OL,10,Fengineering solution that would lead
OL,11,Fto nothing but rainwater entering the
OL,12,Flake."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, an Environment Agency
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We are always
OL,16,Fsaddened to hear of anyone falling ill
OL,17,Fafter visiting our waters. Their
OL,18,Fhealth matters and we remain fully
OL,19,Fcommitted to our ongoing work to
OL,20,Fprotect and improve water quality for
OL,21,Fall.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,F"All four designated bathing waters in
OL,7,FWindermere have been consistently
OL,8,Frated as Excellent since 2015 under
OL,9,Fstrict, legally defined monitoring and
OL,10,Fdata analysis standards that we must
OL,11,Fadhere to.
OL,13,F"We are continuing our extensive
OL,14,Fmonitoring programme in Windermere,
OL,15,Fincluding testing for bacteria that
OL,16,Fcan impact human health on a weekly
OL,17,Fbasis throughout the bathing water
OL,18,Fseason.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774023076
OL,3,CYoung boy hospitalised after kayaking
OL,4,Con Lake Windermere
OL,6,F"We have also deployed additional
OL,7,Fspecialist officers and quadrupled
OL,8,Fwater company inspections in the
OL,9,Fregion in the past twelve months to
OL,10,Froot out wrongdoing and drive better
OL,11,Fperformance."
OL,13,FRex is now doing well, and his mum
OL,14,Fsays "it's looking like he's made a
OL,15,Ffull recovery."
OL,17,FBut what should have been a fondly-
OL,18,Fremembered camping holiday is now an
OL,19,Fordeal the family would rather forget.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
